HEADWORD: Phrasing
<hw>Phras"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Method
of expression; association of words.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Mus.)</fld> <def>The act or method of grouping the
notes so as to form distinct musical phrases.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Phratry</ent>⟦br⟧
